snippet.title: Pax Dei - NVIDIA DLSS 3 Trailer | CES 2024
snippet.description: Take a look at Pax Dei, a medieval flavored social sandbox MMO from developers from Blizzard and Remedy Entertainment. The Mainframe Industries title will hit Early Access on PC this spring, with AI accelerated DLSS 3.
